These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
7 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, snooker, chess, backgammon, scrabble, mah-jongg
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, lily, iris, zinnia, balloon-flower, rose
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person who growsrose is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person playing chess is between the person who growsiris and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person playing snooker##1
11. the person playing scrabble is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person who growsbegonia is the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who growslily and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Game   | canasta  | chess        | monopoly  | mah-jongg     | scrabble   | snooker       | backgammon   |
| Flower         | bellflower   | rose | iris    | lily  | zinnia | balloon-flower | begonia |

