.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, canadian, colombian, egyptian, indian, japanese, thai
7 different games are played: poker, snooker, billiard, scrabble, whist, domino, canasta
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, july, june, march, january, april, november
 1. the canadian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person playing whist is the person playing whist##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person playing poker is the thai##1
 6. the british is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the british is between the person playing canasta and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the indian is on the right of the british##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is the canadian##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
14. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
15. the canadian is on the far right##1
16. the person playing snooker is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai      | egyptian     | british  | indian | colombian | canadian |
| Game         | snooker  | poker | domino | billiard | canasta | scrabble   | whist  |
| Birthday     | june   | april     | november        | march  | january   | july       | december      |

