 7. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is the person playing bridge##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
12. the person playing canasta is the person who likes light-blue##1
13. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
