 3. the person traveling to prague is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to new-york##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person driving the tram is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
12. the person driving the subway is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to rome##2
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
14. the person driving the airplane is the person watching thriller movies##1
15. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
16. the person driving the scooter is the person watching animation movies##1

