15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
16. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person driving the taxi and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku      | skydiving | camping     | woodworking     | drawing   | magic-tricks |
| Transport       | roller    | skateboard | motorbike    | helicopter | van     | jet-ski | taxi |
| Pet        | snake    | goldfish | goat    | rabbit    | guinea-pig | chinchilla | bird |

